productBaseInfoV1.title: Huawei E303C (Hi-Link) Datacard
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Gone are the days when having internet connectivity was a novelty, a service exclusive to a select few. These days, if you do not have the means to stay connected, you are missing out on a lot of opportunities that might help you in your career or social life. The requirement of having an Always On life means you need a piece of equipment that will allow you to stay connected even while on the move. Conventional modems are quickly becoming obsolete, due to the requirement of a cable to stay connected. Some modems have now become more streamlined by doing away with all the wires and hassles associated with them. USB Dongle modems, like the Huawei E303Cs-1 (Hilink Device) Datacard allows you to connect to the internet using your mobile operator’s network. This is achieved by inserting the SIM card of your choice into the proper slot in the Dongle and having access to the network’s data traffic. The Huawei E303Cs-1 (Hilink Device) Datacard is a sleek USB Stick that neatly houses the SIM card slot and Memory Card slot within it. Brought to you by the Chinese Communications company Huawei, the Hilink Device is a reliable piece of equipment that can help you connect to the internet once the necessary configuration has been done on your Laptop, PC or Netbook. The Huawei E303Cs-1 (Hilink Device) Datacard connects to the USB port and is compatible with Windows XP, Vista, and above. It also supports Mac OS 10.5 and 10.6. Linux users will also be able to easily connect to the internet using the Hilink Device. The device supports any 3G or 2G SIM card and this makes it very convenient to choose the best network provider to connect with. This also means that it easily supports your basic GPRS, EDGE and GSM networks. HSUPA, HSDPA and WCDMA are also supported by the Huawei E303Cs-1 (Hilink Device) Datacard giving a good data transfer speed of up to 7.2 Mbps during downloads and up to 5.7 Mbps during uploads provided the network range is at optimum levels. The Huawei E303Cs-1 (Hilink Device) Datacard supports bandwidth ranges of 900 MHz, 1800 MHz, 1900 MHz and 850 MHz on the GSM Network when using EDGE or GPRS. The Huawei E303Cs-1 (Hilink Device) Datacard also acts as a mini storage device, able accommodate MicroSD cards of up to 32 GB of storage capacity. This allows you to use the device like any other USB thumb drive, or pen drive. The external interface is USB 2.0 ready allowing for faster data transfers between the device and your computer. The Huawei E303Cs-1 (Hilink Device) Datacard is a Plug and Play device requiring very simple configuration for first use. The device has an internal antenna which helps in keeping the size small and compact. The device also supports SMS and can be used with 2G, 3G, Dual Band, Tri Band or even Quad Band SIM Cards. It runs on a Balong Chipset which ensures that the device performs smoothly all the time. The Huawei E303Cs-1 (Hilink Device) Datacard is a compact USB Stick with a height of 85.5 mm, width of 27 mm and has a depth of 12.3 mm. The device weighs in at just 30 g. With such a compact design the Datacard is very convenient to carry in a pocket or handbag and is therefore, always on hand for connecting to the information super highway. The device has the capability to go online in just 15 seconds from the time you plug it in, giving you more time to get your work done.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Zyxel GS1100-24 Network Switch
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Affordable Solution for Gigabit Connections to the DesktopThe ZyXEL GS1100 Series is the best solution for instant Gigabit connectivity in office environments demanding silent operation and better energy efficiency. With power-saving functions, Gigabit Ethernet and a fanless design, the GS1100 Series provides plug-and-play simplicity for high-bandwidth network applications.The ZyXEL GS1100 Series consists of four unmanaged switches: the GS1100-8HP, GS1100-16, GS1100-24 and GS1100-24E. The GS1100-16 and GS1100-24E feature 16 and 24 GbE ports. The GS1100-24 is a 24-port Gigabit switch with 2 additional open Gigabit SFP slots, while the GS1100-8HP is an 8-port Gigabit switch that complies with the IEEE 802.3at Power over Ethernet (PoE) Plus standard, providing 4 PoE ports with up to 30 watts per port.Green networkingThe GS1100 Series not only offers Gigabit Ethernet connectivity for next-generation network applications, but also power-saving functions for better energy efficiency. Capable of dynamically adjusting power output according to traffic, active links and cable length, the GS1100 Series can reduce energy consumption for lowered operating costs.Traffic detection ? Energy Efficient Ethernet (EEE) complianceThe IEEE 802.3az Energy Efficient Ethernet (EEE) feature automatically detects network traffic and adjusts power consumption dynamically, enabling the switch to reduce power consumption during low link utilization periods. The GS1100 Series comes with IEEE 802.3az on/off button to help reduce power consumption. This button allows users to keep the best performance without transmit impacted or to have green support of Energy Efficient Ethernet mode with a simple push of a button.Inactive link detectionThe inactive link detection function automatically reduces power usage when inactive links or devices are detected. The ZyXEL GS1100 Series can adjust power consumption according to link status and the number of active network devices.Cable length detectionThis green feature enables the switch to automatically detect the length of connected Ethernet cables and adjust power usage accordingly. The shorter the cable length, the less power it consumes.Fanless designThe complete GS1100 Series comes in a fanless design that ensures silent operation in small or quiet office environments. The GS1100-8HP PoE model is specifically designed with an external power adapter that eliminates the need for an additional fan to cool down the device, making it perfect for quiet PoE deployments.Gigabit to the desktopThe ZyXEL GS1100 Series offers small offices 8/16/24-port Gigabit connectivity at the most competitive price. Additionally, the GS1100-24 model is equipped with 2 extra SFP slots, supported dual rate (100 M and GbE speed) that enable fiber optic connections for long-distance deployments. With Gigabit network performance and high cost-effectiveness, the GS1100 Series is the ideal solution for bandwidth-intensive applications such as high-resolution photo transmission, video/audio streaming and server farm connections.Freedom of installation via PoE (GS1100-8HP)The GS1100-8HP supports the IEEE 802.3at PoE Plus standard to ease the installation of network devices in challenging spaces such as ceilings or walls. The power supply of up to 30 watts per port allows the GS1100-8HP to power PoE-enabled WLAN APs, VoIP phones and IP surveillance cameras through CAT-5 cables of less than 100 meters (300 feet) in length. With the ZyXEL GS1100-8HP, there is no need for extra power adapters in installing PoE devices in difficult locations. This feature helps enterprises reduce installation time and cost when there are many such devices on the networkNon-blocking, wire-speed transmissionAuto MDI/MDI-X supportIEEE 802.3az compliantFanless design for silent runningIEEE 802.3x Flow control supported

General Type :USB 2.0 extension cable.Connections : A plug (flat) to A Socket (Flat) USB v2.0 is a high speed connection method which is 40 times faster than USB v1.1 (480Mbps as opposed to 12Mbps). It is plug & play and hot swappable (no need to turn off your PC to plug a device in or out). It is faster than Firewire (IEEE1394/iLink) but not as qiuck as IEEE1394b (800Mbps). USB v2.0 cables will still work with USB v1.1 computers (they are backwardly compatible) and peripherals, but only if both Computer and Peripheral are USB v2.0 will they work at High Speed (480Mbps). USB v2.0 peripherals will not work at High Speed (480Mbps) unless they are connected with a USB v2.0 cable and connected to a computer equiped with USB v2.0 ports.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Storite 2 Pack Super Flat Hdmi Male To Male Tv Lead 1.4v High Speed Ethernet 3d Full Hd 1080p (150cm - 4.5foot - 1.5m) USB Cable(Yellow)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Premium Quality HDMI-HDMI gold plated Connectors cable suitable for use in HDTV, Plasma, LCD, PS3, Home Theater, Cable box, Projectors and business class projector based applications and more HDMI Ethernet Channel The HDMI 1.4a specification adds a data channel to the HDMI connection, enabling high-speed, bi-directional communication. Connected devices that include this feature can send and receive data via 100 Mb/sec Ethernet, making them instantly ready for any IP-based application. The HDMI Ethernet Channel allows internet-enabled HDMI devices to share an internet connection via the HDMI link, with no need for a separate Ethernet cable. It also provides the connection platform that will allow HDMI-enabled components to share content between devices. Audio Return Channel The new specification adds an audio channel that will reduce the number of cables required to deliver audio "upstream" from a TV to an A/V receiver for processing and playback. In cases where a TV features an internal content source, such as a built-in tuner or DVD player, the Audio Return Channel allows the TV to send audio data upstream to the A/V receiver via the HDMI cable, eliminating the need for an extra cable. 3D The 1.4a version of the specification defines common 3D formats and resolutions for HDMI-enabled devices, enabling 3D gaming and other 3D video applications. The specification standardizes the input/output portion of the home 3D system, facilitating 3D resolutions up to dual-stream 1080p. 4K Resolution Support The new specification enables HDMI devices to support extremely high HD resolutions, effectively four times the resolution of a 1080p device. Support for 4K allows the HDMI interface to transmit digital content at the same resolution as the state-of-the-art Digital Cinema systems used in many movie theaters. Expanded Support For Color Spaces

USB v2.0 peripherals will not work at High Speed (480Mbps) unless they are connected with a USB v2.0 cable and connected to a computer equiped with USB v2.0 ports.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Storite SATA 3 cable with Locking Latch straight to Right Angle 90 Degree (1 Pack Sata 3 Data Cable) Power Cord(Red)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: 40cm SATA 3.0 cable, RIGHT ANGLE 90 degree to straight w/ metal latch,red color SUPER FAST 6GB/S. Backwards compatible with SATA revision 1 and 2 ( SATA I and SATA II). Each major revision of the Serial ATA interface specification has doubled the maximum data transfer rate. The latest SATA Revision 3.0 allows for data transfer speeds of up to 6 Gbps. While the cables for all three revisions appear to be similar and will physically fit into the connectors on all SATA drives and controllers, the higher data transfer rate of SATA 6 Gbps requires higher quality materials and closer tolerances than the previous two revisions required. Storite SATA 6 Gbps cables are certified to provide maximum speeds from your SATA system, up to 6 Gbps when used with equivalent devices and controllers. One end of this internal cable features a straight connector, while the other end uses a 90-degree connector, which can make for better cable management in some situations, especially in tight spaces. Each end has an attached locking latch, to ensure that your connections do not come loose due to movement or vibration. Note that SATA 6 Gbps cables are backwards compatible and can be used with SATA 3 Gbps and SATA 1.5 Gbps devices. However, the data transfer of the SATA subsystem will be limited to that of the slowest device. So, for example, if a SATA 6 Gbps cable is connected to a SATA 3 Gbps drive and a SATA 1.5 Gbps controller, the drive will be limited to a transfer rate of 1.5 Gbps.

While the cables for all three revisions appear to be similar and will physically fit into the connectors on all SATA drives and controllers, the higher data transfer rate of SATA 6 Gbps requires higher quality materials and closer tolerances than the previous two revisions required. Storite SATA 6 Gbps cables are certified to provide maximum speeds from your SATA system, up to 6 Gbps when used with equivalent devices and controllers. One end of this internal cable features a straight connector, while the other end uses a 90-degree connector, which can make for better cable management in some situations, especially in tight spaces. Each end has an attached locking latch, to ensure that your connections do not come loose due to movement or vibration. Note that SATA 6 Gbps cables are backwards compatible and can be used with SATA 3 Gbps and SATA 1.5 Gbps devices. However, the data transfer of the SATA subsystem will be limited to that of the slowest device. So, for example, if a SATA 6 Gbps cable is connected to a SATA 3 Gbps drive and a SATA 1.5 Gbps controller, the drive will be limited to a transfer rate of 1.5 Gbps.

productBaseInfoV1.title: LAVA Pocket Wireless W 150 Router
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: In the age of hyper connectivity and freely available information, technology has made it easier to forge new ways of tapping into the highway. If the connectivity involves wireless technology then the portability of dongles and routers are unmatched. The technology that enables this connection has led to advances that make information freely available to everyone. The Lava W 150 3G supports EVDO and 3G Dongles that can be used with it. The Lava W 150 3G also supports up to 32 users on Local LAN. The Ethernet Support (RJ45) provided by the Lava W 150 3G also comes with Plug and Play. Depending on your connection, the Lava W 150 3G supports speeds of up to 150 Mbps with the WiFi Standard 802.11 b/g/n. The Lava W 150 3G supports software like Internet Explorer, Android, Opera, Chrome, Firefox and Safari. The router supports 3G connectivity which lets you choose the ideal network that suits the area of your residence. The box contains W150 3G Router, a charger, the user Manual, a Warranty Card, the connecting cable with USB support and the Device cover. The device also comes with an LED Indicator that can display the status for the Battery, Power levels, WiFi, Signal Strength and the Network Mode. Lava is the creator of some quality routers that are well made and have excellent reception capabilities. The system operates ideally at humidity levels of 5% to an upper limit of 95%. It works optimally at temperature levels of 0 Degrees Celsius to 70 Degree Celsius. It has idle storage levels ranging from -65 Degrees C to about -125 Degree C. It works on a power supply of 5 V DC, and at 1.5 A. The Lava W 150 3G works with Operating Systems like Windows 7, Windows Vista, Windows XP (SP2 and above). The Lava W 150 3G also supports Android and Mac OS X 10.4.9 – 10.6.0. It connects well using the IEEE 802.11 b/g/n and provides seamless network connection. It runs on a frequency of 2.4 GHz. Due to the high build quality of the Lava W 150 3G, the connection is stable and consistent, peaking at 150 Mbps, which depends on the connection of the network provider you use. The Lava uses 10/100 LAN or WAN connection to deliver blazing speeds for seamless connection. The Lava W 150 3G has one LAN port and 1 USB port with 2.0 USB connection. The LAN connection is with RJ-45. The Lava has Wireless Access Point, Radius Server, Gateways like the TCP / IP are Supported DHCP server is supported, NAT / NAPT is supported. The DNS Relay is Supported on the Lava W 150 3G. SNTP, UPnP, Static Routing, MAC / URL / IP filter is also supported. Battery life on the Lava W 150 3G is impressive with a 4 hours stand alone usage. The battery composition on the Lava is of Lithium Ion, with a 2300 mAH capacity. It has a single SSID Broadcast support with VPN Pass-Through. The Lava W 150 3G is 14.7 mm high, 94 mm wide, and weighs in at 100 g. It has a depth of 61 mm.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Netgear WN1000RP Wi-Fi Booster for Mobile
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Netgear products are extensively used mainly at home and at times, the office as well. They can be employed to boost the WiFi signal that would otherwise be quite weak without an external amplifier. The Netgear WiFi Booster is well suited for Mobile devices and provides an extended coverage at home for areas that are not otherwise accessible for WiFi signals. The Netgear Amplifier helps in extending and strengthening the reach of the base signal or in other words, the existing WiFi signal. This will certainly help in providing an improved wireless experience on iPads, iPhones and Android devices. It is possible to use the Netgear WiFi Booster for Mobile to ramp up your signal so that you can even get access to it around the house and not just within it. The device is best suited for all kinds of mobile devices, like iPads, iPhones, Android tablets, Android Phones and other smartphones as well, like the Windows based Nokia phones. Even Netbooks and other laptops can be connected with the Netgear Booster. The use of the Netgear will be a positive step for those who wish to reduce their mobile data bill. With the extended WiFi connectivity brought forth by the Netgear Booster, you can always switch from expensive mobile data, to the cheaper home based WiFi network. The Booster will also ensure that there are fewer dead zones in the WiFi network present in the house premises. The Booster allows for superior security as well, working with all security standards including WPA-PSK, WPA2-PSK, mixed mode and WEP. The system comes with an Easy Install option, where you do not need the use of a CD or complicated install options. The easy to use Push ‘N’ Connect feature uses the WiFi Protected Setup. This allows for a quick and hassle free secure connection. The universal compatibility of the device also allows you to connect it through signals received from almost any router. These can be from Belkin, Linksys, D-Link, AT&T, 2Wire, Verizon, EarthLink or NETGEAR as well. The Netgear Green features and initiatives include the power button designed to save power, and it also comes in a Recycled Package.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Iball ADSL2 Router(Black)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: This wired networking Router is ideal for basic business, office and home networking amenities. The iBall ADSL2 is a convenient gateway to the Internet or Ethernet for enterprise and entertainment. The IB-LR6111A comes equipped with a Universal Plug and Play (UPnP) server which takes care of its configuration on your PC. The Router complies with the latest ADSL and IEEE 802.3 Protocols to give you seamless Internet connection and wide network coverage. The iBall ADSL2 wired Router comes equipped with a series of firewall, making sure that your network is safe from various Internet threats like phishing and scams. Design This iBall Router is lightweight, and is designed in a sleek horizontal square form factor can be placed comfortably on a table. The front panel of the Router sports 5 LED indicators. These display power status, ADSL status, LAN port indicators, and USB. The dimensions of this router are 174 x 120 x 29 mm. To enhance your networking experience, the iBall Internet gear lets you connect various devices through Ethernet cables. The rear panel of this Router is embedded with 1 RJ11 WAN port, 1 RJ45 LAN port and 1 USB port. Connectivity and Security An advantageous feature of this Router is that it conforms to latest ADSL standards for superior performance up to 24 Mbps downstream. This iBall networking rig also complies with IEEE 802.3 and IEEE 802.3u Protocols delivering a decent performance. This iBall Router is integrated with major security features that include a Stateful Packet Inspection (SPI) firewall, Network Address Translation (NAT) as well as a Packet filter. These features constantly monitor your Internet traffic and keep your computer protected from viruses and other security threats. Features The iBall ADSL2 Router is equipped with IGMP snooping which is an Internet Group Management Protocol that allows a network switch to 'listen' to conversations between hosts and Routers. This, in turn, further assists in keeping a track of multicast or information traffic. The integrated Dynamic Host Configuration Protocol (DHCP) server of this Router helps manage Internet Protocol networks that must be configured before they can communicate with other hosts connected to your Router. Furthermore, the Router also has the option of Web Based management control.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Storite SATA 3 cable with Locking Latch straight to Right Angle 90 Degree - Black (30cm) Power Cord(Black)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: SATA 3.0 cable, RIGHT ANGLE to straight w/ metal latch,black color SUPER FAST 6GB/S. Backwards compatible with SATA revision 1 and 2 (SATA I and SATA II). Each major revision of the Serial ATA interface specification has doubled the maximum data transfer rate. The latest SATA Revision 3.0 allows for data transfer speeds of up to 6 Gbps. While the cables for all three revisions appear to be similar and will physically fit into the connectors on all SATA drives and controllers, the higher data transfer rate of SATA 6 Gbps requires higher quality materials and closer tolerances than the previous two revisions required. Storite SATA 6 Gbps cables are certified to provide maximum speeds from your SATA system, up to 6 Gbps when used with equivalent devices and controllers. One end of this internal cable features a straight connector, while the other end uses a 90-degree connector, which can make for better cable management in some situations, especially in tight spaces. Each end has an attached locking latch, to ensure that your connections do not come loose due to movement or vibration. Note that SATA 6 Gbps cables are backwards compatible and can be used with SATA 3 Gbps and SATA 1.5 Gbps devices. However, the data transfer of the SATA subsystem will be limited to that of the slowest device. So, for example, if a SATA 6 Gbps cable is connected to a SATA 3 Gbps drive and a SATA 1.5 Gbps controller, the drive will be limited to a transfer rate of 1.5 Gbps.

Model: SATA 3 cable with Locking Latch straight to Right Angle 90 Degree - Black (30cm)

productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: DVI-D Dual link cables are much higher rated on bandwidth (up to 2560 x 1600 resolution / 1600p) compared to single link which is only rated up to 1920x1200 resolutions. This cable is mostly used for connecting your Xbox 360, Playstation 3, DSTV HDPVR, Blu-ray player to a display with only DVI-D input and no HDMI inputs. Audio will travel via coaxial / optical since HDMI to DVI only carries video. Smaller computer LCD Screens are much cheaper compared to LCD TV's and offers much higher resolutions than normal televisions. Plug cable from Output HDMI Female on HDMI Device to Input Female DVI-D on display. The cable is bi-directional and can also by used to connect your PC Graphics Card (DVI Output) to the HDMI Port on your HDMI display. The graphics card output needs to support DVI-D digital signals. Most Nvidia and ATI graphics cards support DVI-I which can autoswitch between DVI-D (Digital) and DVI-A (Analog).

Model: Premium Quality High Speed Gold Plated HDMI to DVI-D Dual Link Cable 24+1
